# 3.3 Layered Architecture

The application consists of seven logical layers.

```
+------------------------------------------------+
|                Presentation Layer              |
|           HTML / CSS / Flask UI                |
+------------------------------------------------+

+------------------------------------------------+
|               API Layer                        |
|                Flask Routes                    |
+------------------------------------------------+

+------------------------------------------------+
|              Agent Layer                       |
|                Google ADK                      |
+------------------------------------------------+

+------------------------------------------------+
|            Reasoning Layer                     |
|             Gemini 2.5 Flash                   |
+------------------------------------------------+

+------------------------------------------------+
|              Tool Layer                        |
|              MCP Servers                       |
+------------------------------------------------+

+------------------------------------------------+
|          External Services Layer               |
|   Tavily | Google Maps | Scholarship Server    |
+------------------------------------------------+

+------------------------------------------------+
|             Output Layer                       |
| Markdown Report + Final Response               |
+------------------------------------------------+
```

Each layer has a single responsibility.

This makes the system modular and easier to maintain.

