---

# 3.9 Final Architecture Summary

The final system demonstrates a modern AI architecture in which:

- Flask manages web requests.
- Google ADK manages orchestration.
- Gemini performs reasoning.
- MCP servers perform execution.
- Docker guarantees environment consistency.
- Render hosts the application.
- Specialized tools collaborate to solve complex user requests.

The resulting application is modular, extensible, and representative of the architectural patterns used in enterprise-grade AI systems that rely on tool augmentation rather than model-only intelligence.